data.title: 输出是什么？
data.desc:
```javascript
function getPersonInfo(one, two, three) {
  console.log(one)
  console.log(two)
  console.log(three)
}

const person = 'Lydia'
const age = 21

getPersonInfo`${person} is ${age} years old`
```
data.options: {"options":["\"Lydia\" 21 [\"\", \" is \", \" years old\"]","[\"\", \" is \", \" years old\"] \"Lydia\" 21","\"Lydia\" [\"\", \" is \", \" years old\"] 21"],"isMulti":false,"answer":[1]}
data.explanation: 如果使用标记模板字面量，第一个参数的值总是包含字符串的数组。其余的参数获取的是传递的表达式的值！
